OL,6,F"For me that was one of the first
OL,7,Fmoments where I became interested in
OL,8,Fpolitics. It matters who holds
OL,9,Fpositions, who wins elections, who
OL,10,Fgoes to Westminster. It matters."
OL,12,FNow 28, Lloyd was born at Dorset
OL,13,FCounty Hospital and grew up in
OL,14,FWeymouth. At weekends he worked with
OL,15,Fhis Dad in the Marlboro, a popular
OL,16,Fchippy by the seafront. It's a bit of
OL,17,Fa family affair. Hatton jokes: "I
OL,18,Fthink my dad actually proposed to my
OL,19,Fmum around the back!"
