OL,3,CThe young MP that's swapped working in
OL,4,Ca chippy for Parliament
OL,6,FLabour's historic landslide on 5 July
OL,7,Fsaw Keir Starmer's Party take seats
OL,8,Ffrom the Conservatives that even they
OL,9,Fweren't expecting to win.
OL,11,FDespite previously being held by
OL,12,FLabour, the South Dorset seat was
OL,13,Fconsidered fairly safe for the Tories,
OL,14,Fhaving been held by Richard Drax for
OL,15,F14 years.
OL,17,FIt was a closely fought battle, but
OL,18,FHatton won with 15,659 votes and a
OL,19,Fmajority of 1,048.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
