OL,6,F"We knew it was always going to be a
OL,7,Fbig challenge to win here, but we knew
OL,8,Fwe had won here before," Hatton
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,F"I think people were looking for that
OL,12,Fchange. We felt that when we were
OL,13,Ftalking to voters and listening to
OL,14,Fvoters on the doorstep. And lots of
OL,15,Fpeople looked to Labour to deliver
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
