OL,6,F"l never really ever considered
OL,7,Fstanding anywhere else before. I
OL,8,Fthought if I was going to do this it
OL,9,Fhas to be at home where all my
OL,10,Ffriends, my family, my neighbours are.
OL,11,FFor me it's a real proud moment to
OL,12,Frepresent my community."
OL,14,FThe South Dorset constituency is
OL,15,Flargely known as an outstanding
OL,16,Fholiday hotspot with the Jurassic
OL,17,FCoast, Lulworth Cove and Durdle Door,
OL,18,Fbut it has most recently been in the
OL,19,Fspotlight for housing the
OL,20,Fcontroversial Bibby Stockholm barge
OL,21,Ffor asylum seekers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
