OL,6,FAccording to the Home Office, the
OL,7,Fasylum applications of those on board
OL,8,Fwill now be processed with extreme
OL,9,F"urgency".
OL,11,FAs of the end of July, #218,208 has
OL,12,Fbeen spent in three months by Dorset
OL,13,FCouncil, on costs related to the barge
OL,14,Fand housing the asylum seekers.
OL,16,FOn the issue of dwindling public trust
OL,17,Fin elected MPs, 28-year-old Hatton
OL,18,Facknowledged it's a "huge issue" and
OL,19,Fone that needs to be tackled by all
OL,20,Fparties.
